rComments: Almut is easily one of the best professors I've had at UofT! She has very energetic and entertaining math lectures, and you can tell how much care she puts into her problem sets!

A wonderful professor -- extremely friendly, passionate, and willing to devote office hrs to helping students.  Also, she's very reasonable in what she expects from student; her math course actually ended with a C average, whereas Uppal or Cohen would have left it at a D.  Finally, her problems were *very* clever, and very fun to solve.
